These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
2 different pets are kept: dog, snake
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, february
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is not the owner of the snake##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | snake   | dog  |
| Sport   | july | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, german
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, lily
1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growsazalea is not the german##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | canadian | german      |
| Pet    | azalea  | lily |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
