There are 2 different nationalities: polish, thai
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the polish is not the person driving the jet-ski##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | snowmobile  | jet-ski    |
| Sport   | polish | thai |

