.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, fantasy
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate
1. the person watching fantasy movies is not the person drinking lemonade##6
2. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | drama  | fantasy |
| Pet    | lemonade | hot-chocolate    |

